# Event-Driven Rules

- Emit domain events for significant business transitions.
- Keep event payloads stable and versioned when externally consumed.
- Handlers must be idempotent and safe under at-least-once delivery.
- Use outbox-style reliability patterns for critical integration events.
- Avoid putting heavy business logic directly inside event listeners.
